  "text": "The final stage of the framework aims to build supervised topic classifiers corresponding to the different cross-source scenarios, which make use of the generated KS semantic features. The Support Vector Machine (SVM) ( [CITATION_1] ) with polynomial kernel was selected as a base classifier, which we detail in Section 8.",
